# Skill Authoring Guidelines

Guidelines for creating effective Cursor skills, based on the [Agent Skills specification](https://agentskills.io/specification) and [Anthropic best practices](https://platform.claude.com/docs/en/agents-and-tools/agent-skills/best-practices).

